data.text:
Exclusive collection for fans only at famecollectibles.com! Photo Jigsaw Puzzles. Choose from large or small, 120 pieces or 300 pieces full-color, photo quality collector jigsaw puzzles.

Description

Available in two sizes:

120 pieces: Small Fun Size puzzle, size: 7.75″x11.75″

300 pieces: Large Challenge puzzle, size 11.5″x16″

Photo quality image on vivid gloss puzzle board.

Special Challenge Pieces: Puzzle pieces are of a similar shape which makes it extra challenging.

Recommended age 13+. Puzzles ship partially assembled to ensure all pieces arrive intact. Gently break apart pieces when ready to assemble.

Unique gift you won’t find anywhere else!

When finished, your puzzle can be framed as a permanent work of art.

Unique GIft item exclusive to Famecollectibles.com

Additional information

Weight 12 oz Dimensions 9 × 6 × 1 in Size

120 pcs, 300 pcs
